      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(feishu): disable ambient proxy inheritance for websocket by default",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Disable Feishu WebSocket ambient proxy inheritance by default.\n- Add `OPENCLAW_FEISHU_WS_USE_PROXY=1` as the explicit opt-in for Feishu WS proxy routing.\n- Cover default/no-proxy and opt-in proxy behavior in Feishu client tests.\n\nCloses #65799.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- **Behavior or issue addressed:** Feishu WebSocket should not inherit ambient `HTTPS_PROXY` / `https_proxy` by default. It should only use ambient proxy env when `OPENCLAW_FEISHU_WS_USE_PROXY=1`.\n- **Real environment tested:** macOS local OpenClaw worktree, real `@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk` `WSClient`, real `@openclaw/proxyline` ambient proxy agent, local TLS `wss://` server, local HTTP proxy recording `CONNECT`.\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch:** Ran a local proof script that starts a temporary `wss://127.0.0.1:<port>` WebSocket server and temporary HTTP proxy, sets `https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:<proxyPort>`, then connects once without a WS agent and once with the ambient proxy agent.\n- **Evidence after fix:**\n\n```text\ndefault ambient env, no ws agent:\n  stateAfterReady: connected\n  wsConnectionsDelta: 1\n  proxyEvents: []\n  agentConstructed: false\n\nexplicit opt-in agent from ambient env:\n  stateAfterReady: connected\n  wsConnectionsDelta: 1\n  proxyEvents:\n    CONNECT 127.0.0.1:<port>\n  agentConstructed: true\n```\n\n- **Observed result after fix:** Ambient proxy env no longer affects Feishu WS by default; explicit opt-in routes the same WS connection through the proxy.\n- **What was not tested:** No live Feishu production app credentials were used; the proof isolates the WebSocket/proxy transport behavior with a local TLS WS endpoint.\n\n## Verification\n\n```text\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.extension-feishu.config.ts extensions/feishu/src/client.test.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  16 passed (16)\n```\n\n```text\nnode scripts/run-oxlint.mjs --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.extensions.json extensions/feishu/src/client.ts extensions/feishu/src/client.test.ts\nFound 0 warnings and 0 errors.\n```\n\n```text\nnode scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p extensions/feishu/tsconfig.json --noEmit\n```\n",
